FBIS3-37040 "drsov030_b_94011" FBIS-SOV-94-030 Document Type:Daily Report 14 Feb 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Two Deputy Finance Ministers Quit MK1102092094 Moscow KURANTY in Russian 11 Feb 94 p 1 MK1102092094 Moscow KURANTY Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Unattributed report under the "Behind the Scenes" rubric: "Reformers' Resignations Continue"] [Text] Andrey Illarionov's resignation from the government has proven to be far from the last one. KURANTY has come to learn that two deputy finance ministers at once -- Kuzmin and Aleksashin -- have submitted their resignation. Unfortunately, the prognoses by experts, who thought that Boris Fedorov's departure would enable the premier, in league with the Agrarians, to crush with no special effort the resistance of the last bastion on the road to hyperinflation, are beginning to come true.
